io.raffi.JSON

Class JSONData

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.raffi.JSON.JSONData

  • public class JSONData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is very important, because it wraps the JSON data into it. It can be a base type, or an array or object. This object can be used for the high level iterations as a base type. This class is able to return the original data type, or it can cast it for the caller if applicable.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Rafael Grigorian
